<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>彭博加密货币</title><link>https://bloomberg.com/crypto/</link><description>彭博加密货币</description><lastBuildDate>Tue, 14 Jul 2026 13:02:13 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>CleanSpark 同意以 66 亿美元租用为期 20 年的数据中心</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-07-14/cleanspark-agrees-20-year-data-center-lease-for-6-6-billion</link><description>比特币矿商 CleanSpark Inc. 已同意以 66 亿美元的合同收入为其位于佐治亚州桑德斯维尔园区的数据中心提供为期 20 年的基础设施租赁。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/ivVBIg1aRRhQ/v1/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 14 Jul 2026 10:00:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-07-14/cleanspark-agrees-20-year-data-center-lease-for-6-6-billion</guid></item><item><title>Polymarket 在世界杯半决赛期间与加密货币公司合作</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-07-14/polymarket-partners-with-crypto-firm-during-world-cup-semifinals</link><description>加密货币经纪公司 Blockchain.com Group Holdings Inc. 已与 Polymarket 合作，及时为其用户提供世界杯半决赛的预测市场。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/i0tODVa6HnvU/v1/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 14 Jul 2026 10:00:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-07-14/polymarket-partners-with-crypto-firm-during-world-cup-semifinals</guid></item><item><title>油价飙升引发通胀担忧，比特币走弱</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-07-13/bitcoin-weakens-as-oil-price-spike-revives-inflation-concerns</link><description>在美国对伊朗发动新的袭击后，油价飙升，比特币周一下跌，引发了人们对能源成本上升可能会重新带来通胀压力并抑制对风险资产的需求的担忧。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iQM8fAzKiPzo/v2/1200x-1.png" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 13 Jul 2026 04:48:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-07-13/bitcoin-weakens-as-oil-price-spike-revives-inflation-concerns</guid></item><item><title>Strategy 通过出售股票将储备金提高至 30 亿美元</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-07-13/saylor-s-strategy-raises-reserve-to-3-billion-with-stock-sale</link><description>Michael Saylor 的 Strategy Inc. 通过出售普通股筹集了约 4.67 亿美元，将其现金储备增加至约 30 亿美元，同时避免买卖比特币。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/i3BHlXuTCKXI/v2/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 13 Jul 2026 12:41:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-07-13/saylor-s-strategy-raises-reserve-to-3-billion-with-stock-sale</guid></item><item><title>华尔街对万亿美元稳定币热潮发起阻力</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-07-13/wall-street-mounts-pushback-on-trillion-dollar-stablecoin-boom</link><description>多年来，银行在很大程度上目睹了稳定币从一种利基加密货币产品发展成为每年交易量数十万亿美元的支付网络。现在，他们正在重新制定与 Zelle 相同的协作策略，押注共享基础设施是阻止数字美元进一步蚕食他们业务的最佳方式。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/i8oewQVC2gFM/v9/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 13 Jul 2026 12:03:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-07-13/wall-street-mounts-pushback-on-trillion-dollar-stablecoin-boom</guid></item></channel></rss>